TITLE: Generating Image with AI in Activepieces (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to generate an image using AI within Activepieces. It uses the `AI` class to interact with an AI provider and the `image.generate` method to create an image based on a prompt, model, and other options. It requires `context.propsValue` to access configuration values and `context.server` for server-related functionalities.
SOURCE: https://github.com/activepieces/activepieces/blob/main/docs/developers/unified-ai/image.mdx#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
const ai = AI({
  provider: context.propsValue.provider,
  server: context.server,
});

const response = await image.generate({
  // The model to use for image generation
  model: context.propsValue.model,
  // The prompt to guide the image generation
  prompt: context.propsValue.prompt,
  // The resolution of the generated image
  size: "1024x1024",
  // Any advanced options for the image generation
  advancedOptions: {},
});
```

